This simple project uses express, body-parser, ejs and axios to return the 
price_24h, volume_24h and last_trade_price of several cryptocurrencies using
the blockchain.com REST API: https://api.blockchain.com/v3/

To install this project and run it:

1. git clone the project to your local working directory.
2. in VSCode terminal: npm install
3. in VSCode terminal: nodemon index.js
4. in Chrome, go to URL: localhost:3000
